def has_toaster(kitchen_counter:item):
    # Function to check if there is a toaster on the kitchen counter
    symbol has_toaster=exists toaster:item : is_toaster(toaster) and on(toaster, kitchen_counter)
    return has_toaster

behavior toast_bread(bread:item, toaster:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(bread, toaster)
        # Put the bread in the toaster

        achieve is_on(toaster)
        # Turn on the toaster to start toasting

behavior prepare_and_toast_bread(bread:item):
    body:
        bind kitchen_counter: item where:
            is_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter)

        if has_toaster(kitchen_counter):
            bind toaster: item where:
                is_toaster(toaster) and on(toaster, kitchen_counter)
            toast_bread(bread, toaster)
        else:
            # If no toaster is found on the known kitchen counter, initiate exploration to locate on
e
            foreach kitchen_counter: item:
                if is_kitchen_counter(kitchen_counter) and not visited(kitchen_counter):
                    observe(kitchen_counter, "Check if there is a toaster on the kitchen counter")
                    if has_toaster(kitchen_counter):
                        bind toaster: item where:
                            is_toaster(toaster) and on(toaster, kitchen_counter)
                        toast_bread(bread, toaster)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind food_bread: item where:
            is_food_bread(food_bread) and cut(food_bread)
        # Select the already sliced bread
        
        prepare_and_toast_bread(food_bread)
